parameters: \FF[yuri_tyu]???: "You shouldn't run in the hallways. It's bad manners."
\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[yuri_tyu]\AA[2]???: "Especially in a hospital. Don't you understand that?"

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[yuri_tyu]\AA[2]???: "If you want to play, there should be more appropriate
places. Like a park, for example. If you run around in a
place like this..."

\F[beni_angrytyu]\FF[yuri_tyu]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Even so... no matter how much I know it's
wrong... there are times when I just can't hold back!"
\F[beni_smiletyu]Akane Suzaku: "Haha! I see... so that's what it is...!"

\F[beni_smiletyu]\FF[yuri_tyu]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "Thank you!! I couldn't have understood...
what it's like when straying from the path becomes the
norm..."

\F[beni_troubletyu]\FF[yuri_tyu]\AA[1]Akane Suzaku: "You're the same. Unable to empathize with
those who are hurt or feel guilty. You can't even imagine
it."

\FF[yuri_tyu]???: "To make straying from the path the norm...? But that
would disrupt order."

\FF[yuri_tyu]???: "However... there are people who must live that way...
I see..."

\FF[yuri_tyu]???: "To reconcile such contradictions... I must first
understand... the meaning of running in the hallways!!"
